data.description: Looking to live Florida lifestyle as its best?  Enjoy the beauty of the Florida outdoors with a boat dock to build in your backyard and feel the relaxation of canal water views from your living room. This exquisite home offers a perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and modern living. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a bright and airy living space with high ceilings and interior doors, accentuated by the modern lighting fixtures that create an inviting atmosphere.   The kitchen is the heart of this pristine Home that features amazing upgrades like quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, accent wall in living room, ceramic tiles floors that add warmth and character, all bathrooms were upgraded to showers. Step outside to your outdoor oasis, where you can unwind with a screened in patio that comes pre-plumbed for a future outdoor kitchen or enjoy the lush green backyard. There's plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or even the possibility of a future pool. Canals weave throughout the community to connect residents’ backyards to a 3,400-acre lake and its chain of lakes. In addition to the natural beauty of the area, you can enjoy the resort-style zero-entry (beach-entry) pool and splash pad and Water Park or gather on the expansive sundeck with views of the community. Hanover Lakes offers a convenient location in beautiful Osceola County. Home comes equipped with washer and dryer, Water softener system, Solar panels and amazing neighbors! Assumable FHA Mortgage at 3.5% and Sellers are offering $10,000 Buyer Concession towards closing costs, pre-paids or buy down the rate!   Discover the possibilities of lakeside living at Hanover Lakes. Don't miss my 3D Virtual Tour: https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=fFQZ9y8fnzU&mls=1
